---
import LegalLayout from '../components/LegalLayout.astro';
---
<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Designed to Elevate handles personal information collected through this website and during client engagements."
  pathname="privacy"
  intro="This page explains what information Designed to Elevate collects, how it is used, and the choices you have."
>
  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <p>
    When you submit a quote request or contact form, we collect the information you provide — typically your name,
    business name, email address, phone number, website URL, and any details you share about your project.
  </p>
  <p>
    Standard server and analytics logs may collect basic technical information such as browser type, device,
    referring page, and pages visited. This is used to understand site usage and improve the site.
  </p>

  <h2>How we use information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To respond to your inquiry and provide a quote</li>
    <li>To deliver services you have engaged us to perform</li>
    <li>To communicate about active projects and follow-ups</li>
    <li>To improve the website and services</li>
    <li>To meet legal, accounting, and tax obligations</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Sharing</h2>
  <p>
    We do not sell personal information. We may share information with service providers we use to operate our
    business — for example, hosting, email, analytics, or payment processing — only to the extent necessary to
    provide our services and under reasonable confidentiality expectations.
  </p>

  <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
  <p>
    The site may use cookies or similar technologies for basic analytics and to maintain site functionality.
    You can control cookies through your browser settings.
  </p>

  <h2>Your choices</h2>
  <p>
    You can request access, correction, or deletion of personal information you have provided by emailing us
    at <a href="mailto:bilsonxnc@gmail.com">bilsonxnc@gmail.com</a>. We will respond within a reasonable time.
  </p>

  <h2>Children</h2>
  <p>
    The site and services are not directed to children under 13 and we do not knowingly collect personal
    information from them.
  </p>

  <h2>Updates to this policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this policy from time to time. The effective date above will reflect the most recent revision.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about this policy can be sent to
    <a href="mailto:bilsonxnc@gmail.com">bilsonxnc@gmail.com</a>
    or by phone at <a href="tel:+17406176488">740-617-6488</a>.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
